    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\ude97 You have got to see this beauty! It\u2019s honestly in absolutely pristine condition\u2014I\u2019ve babied it from day one and it looks like it just rolled off the showroom floor. No scratches, no dents, just pure perfection. I'm looking for a smooth sale, so I've priced it to move! Come take it for a spin and see for yourself why I'm so excited about it. Let's get you behind the wheel! \u2728",
