    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offering a collector-grade 2004 BMW M3 (E46) in pristine mechanical and cosmetic order. This example features the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six, utilizing individual throttle bodies and a dual-VANOS system that has been professionally overhauled to ensure optimal cam timing and torque delivery. Power is managed through a precise Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox and a factory-calibrated Variable M Differential Lock. Crucially, the chassis has undergone proactive subframe reinforcement with structural plates, and the rod bearings have been replaced with updated coated shells to ensure longevity. The suspension geometry is maintained by fresh OEM bushings and dampers, preserving the iconic 50/50 weight distribution. This is a zero-leak, zero-fault vehicle with a clean underside and a flawless engine bay, representing the zenith of naturally aspirated M-division performance.",
      "price": 46500.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 43
    },
    {
