    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m honestly so sad to see this beauty go, but it\u2019s time for someone else to enjoy it. This car is in absolutely incredible shape\u2014honestly, it feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor! It\u2019s been babied since day one, kept in a garage, and looks stunning inside and out. If you\u2019re looking for something that\u2019s been cared for with a lot of love, this is the one. Come take a look and fall in love!",
      "price": 44500.0,
