    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Offered is an investment-grade E46 M3, showcasing the pinnacle of the S54 platform. This example features a meticulously maintained 3.2L atmospheric inline-six with individual throttle bodies, delivering linear power up to its 8,000 RPM redline. Critical preventative maintenance has been performed, including a comprehensive rod bearing replacement and a Besian Systems VANOS overhaul. The chassis integrity is guaranteed via documented rear subframe reinforcement. Power is managed through a tactile Getrag 6-speed manual transmission and a factory M-variable limited-slip differential. The exterior paint depth is consistent across all panels with no clear coat failure, and the interior remains in a preserved state with supple Nappa leather and zero bolster wear. This is a mechanically superlative specimen for the serious collector.",
